NAME: kick
DESCRIPTION: Kick an user from the server.
OPTIONS_USER_DESCRIPTION: The user to kick from the server.
OPTIONS_NOTIFY_DESCRIPTION: Whether to notify the user of the kick.
OPTIONS_VISIBLE_DESCRIPTION: Whether to show the kick in the channel.
KICKED: **An user has been kicked from the server.**
PERMISSIONS: The user you want to kick either have a higher role than you or the bot doesn't have the permissions to kick them.
NOT_MEMBER: The user you want to kick is not a member of the server.
